notes.value:
"Cā kraññʻʹ tuikʻ Paññā Dīpaluimā Bhvaiʹ ʼa tvakʻ lui ʼapʻ khyakʻ myāʺ e* tacʻ citʻ tacʻ desa ʼāʺ phraṅʻʹ ī kyamʻʺ ṅayʻ kui taṅʻ svaṅʻʺ pā saññʻ."
